Okuzuula obulwadde obwesigika kulina kwesigama ku muntu eyeekweka alina ekimu ku bubonero buno oba omusaayi ogwesigamiziddwa ku: (1) Okuzuula kwa PCR mu kiseera ekituufu okwalaga obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2; (2) okukwata ku bitundu bya kawuka ebiraga nti birina akakwate n'akawuka akalala ak'akawuka akalala akazuulibwa; (3) okulaga obulwadde ku sseroomu eya IgM ne IgG eri SARS-CoV-2; oba okukyusa mu sseroomu eya IgG eya SARS-CoV-2 okuva mu bantu abatalina bulwadde okudda mu balwadde, oba okwongera mu kifo kimu okusinga emirundi 4 mu kitundu ekirongooka mu kiseera eky'obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
