Nga Maaki 17, Adam Kucharski owa London School of Hygiene &amp; Tropical Medicine yagamba nti SARS-CoV-2 ejja kusenguka okuva mu kifo ekimu okudda mu kirala, oboolyawo okumala omwaka gumu oba ebiri.
