Amaduuka ag'emmere agataaliimu bantu gaaliwo okumala akaseera katono, era ne mu kibuga Wuhan, ab'obuyinza mu China baagagulawo amaduuka ag'emmere y'embizzi okulabirira abantu.
Amateeka ag'enjawulo galiwo mu Italy nga galagira abalimi ba mmere okukuuma ebirungo byabwe nga bisobola okuyitibwa mu mbeera ez'amaanyi.
Obuzibu mu by'enfuna mu nsi yonna bwasosonkera ne mu China: okusinziira ku lipoota za bannamawulire nga Maaki 16, eby'enfuna mu China byagwa mu myezi ebiri egyasooka egy'omwaka 2020 olw'enteekateeka z'obufuzi ez'okutangira ekirwadde kino okusaasaana, era n'obusuubuzi obwavaamu bwagwa ebitundu 20.5%.
Olw'okuba China ya maanyi mu by'enfuna ne mu by'amakolero, ekirwadde kino kyalabika ng'ekikulu ennyo mu by'enfuna by'ensi yonna.
Agathe Demarais owa The Economist yagamba nti ebyenfuna bijja kweyongera okutabuka okutuusa ng'ekifaananyi ekituufu ku bibala ebiyinza okuvaamu kyeyolese.
Mu January 2020, abeekenneenya abamu baalagula nti obuzibu bw'eby'enfuna obuvudde ku kawumpuli obwo buyinza okuba nga businga obw'ekirwadde kya SARS ekyaliwo mu 2002-2004.
Ekimu ku byokulabirako ebyaweebwa abakugu ku Washington University e St. Louis kiraga obuzibu bwa doola ezisukka mu buwumbi 300 ku nnyingiza y'ensi yonna era kino kiyinza okumalawo emyaka ebiri.
Kigambibwa nti ekibiina kya OPEC "kyasobeddwa nnyo" oluvannyuma lw'ebbeeyi y'amafuta okukendeera olw'okuba China yali teyeetabye.
Nga Febwali 24, ebyenfuna n'emisolo by'ensi yonna byagwa olw'okweyongera kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 ebweru wa China.
Nga Febwali 27, olw'okweraliikirira okw'obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe, ebitabo by'ebyenfuna eby'enjawulo mu Amerika, omuli NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 Index, ne Dow Jones Industrial Average, byafulumya ebitundu ebikyasinze okugwa okuva mu 2008, nga Dow ekendeera ebitundu 1,191, ebitundu ebikyasinze okugwa mu lunaku lumu okuva ku ntandikwa y'obuzibu bw'eby'enfuna mu 2007-08.
Ebisaanyizo byonna ebisatu byaggwa wiiki nga biri wansi wa 10%.
Nga 28 Febwali, Scope Ratings GmbH yakakasa ekitongole kya China eky'obusika, kyokka ne kiba nti tekyali kirungi.
Empeereza n'emisolo byagwa olw'okutya akawuka ka coronavirus, nga ekisinga okugwa ku 16 March.
Abantu bangi balowooza nti embeera y'eby'enfuna ejja kutereera.
Omwekenneenya w'eby'enfuna Mohamed El-Erian asiima bbanka enkulu n'abafuzi olw'okuyamba mu kiseera ekituufu.
