bAngiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enziina ekola ensimbi ekwata ku bitundu by'omubiri eby'ebweru (ebisenge by'omubiri) eby'omubiri mu biwundu, emisono gy'omusaayi, omutima, ensigo, n'ebisenge.
ACE2 ekendeeza ku bikolwa bya enzyme ey'okufuula angiotensin (ACE) ng'ekendeeza omuwendo gwa angiotensin-II n'okuleeta Ang (((1-7) n'ekifuula eddagala eryesigika erijjanjaba obulwadde bw'omutima.ACE2 era eyamba ng'omulyango oguyingira mu mubiri ku coronaviruses ezimu.
Enkola y'omuntu ey'ekitooke kino kitera okuyitibwa hACE2.
Ensawo ya angiotensin-con 2 erimu enzyme ey'ekyuma ekirimu zinki era esangibwa ku bitundu by'ensiri n'ensiri endala.
ACE2 erimu ekitundu kya N-terminal peptidase M2 ne C-terminal collectrin ekitwala eddagala mu nsigo.
ACE2 y'ekika kya proteini eya type I ekikola ekkubo limu, nga ekitundu kyayo eky'ekika kya proteini ekikola ekikola ku bitundu by'omubiri eby'omu biwundu n'ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ACE2 ekisangibwa ku lusegere lw'ensulo kiwandika ku lusegere lw'ensulo ne ku proteini endala ey'ekika ky'ensulo eyitibwa sheddase, era proteini eyo esobola okuvunda n'eyingira mu kkubo ery'omubiri ne liggyibwa mu lubuto.
ACE2 erina ebitundu bingi eby'omubiri: ACE2 ekwata ku butonde bw'omubiri naddala obutoffaali bw'omubiri obw'ekika II, obutoffaali bw'omubiri, obutoffaali bw'omusaayi n'obutonde bw'omubiri, n'obutoffaali bw'omusaayi mu bitundu by'omubiri bingi.
ACE2 mRNA expression esangibwa ku mutimbagano gw'obwongo, ku striatum, ku hypothalamus, ne ku ssenge.
Omulimu ogusooka ogwa ACE2 kwe kuteekawo omutindo gwa ACE.
ACE ekwata ku angiotensin I ne angiotensin II ekendeeza ku musaayi.
ACE2 nayo ekendeeza ku phenylalanine eya carboxyl-terminal amino acid okuva ku angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era ne yeeyungamu ne angiotensin eri mu mitendera eminene egy'omusaayi (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 era esobola okuvvuunula peptide nga [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, ne ghrelin.
ACE2 era ekubiriza omutambuzi wa amino acid omutambuze SLC6A19 okukola obulungi era erina kinene ky'ekola mu bulwadde bwa Hartnup obuleeta protein.
Ng'obutonde obw'obutonde obw'omulembe, ACE2 ekola ng'omulyango omukulu mu butoffaali obuzingiramu koronavairusi ezimu, gamba nga HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (akawuka akaviirako SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akaviirako COVID-19).
Mu ngeri ey'enkukunala, akakwate kaaliwo wakati w'okuyitibwa kwa SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 S1 protein mu kifo kya ACE2 ku butoffaali obwa endocytosis n'okusenguka kwa virus okuva mu kifo kyayo n'okufuuka butoffaali obwa hormone okudda mu butoffaali obwa selula.
Enkola eno era eragira protein S okukola ku TMPRSS2 era okunoonyereza kuyinza okugilemesa okukola nga ekkubo ekkulu ery'okujjanjaba. Kino kyabaleetera okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku ACE2 mu butoffaali, kiyinza okuyamba okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina bingi eby'enjawulo n'ebitongole ebikuuma ddembe byasaba okuteekawo enkola ey'okuziyiza ACE okukola ku ddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba ARB.
Okunoonyereza okwaliwo nga tekukwatagana na kuno okwaliwo nga July 11, 2012, kwalaga nti "okukozesa eddagala erirwanyisa ACE kukwataganyizibwa n'okukendeeza ku kabi ka ssennyiga ku bitundu 34% bw'okugeraageranya n'abo abalabirirwa".
Ate era, "obubenje bw'obulwadde bw'obwongo bwakendeera nnyo mu balwadde abaliko obuzibu obw'amaanyi abajjanjabibwa eddagala erirwanyisa ACE naddala abalwadde b'omutima n'abo abalina obulwadde bw'omutima obutali bumu.
Okukozesa eddagala erirwanyisa ACE era kwaleetebwawo okukendeeza ku kufa okuva mu busaasizi, wadde ng'ebyavaamu tebyali bya maanyi okusinga akabi ak'obulwadde bwa busaasizi".
ACE2 (rhACE2) ekikozesebwa mu bujjanjabi ekiragibwa okuba ekirwadde ekiruma ennyo mu biwundu era kirabika kyongera ku musaayi oguyita mu biwundu n'okuyamba mu kuzzaawo obutonotono mu bitundu ebirimu obuwuka obuviirako ekiwundu.
Ekitundu ky'obulamu bw'eddagala ery'okuzza rhACE2 mu bantu kiri essaawa 10 era litandika okukola eddakiika 30 oluvannyuma lw'ekiseera eky'essaawa 24 ng'ebiva mu ddagala eryo bitandise okweyoleka.
Okunoonyereza okuwerako kulaga nti rhACE2 esobola okuba eddagala ery'essuubi eri abantu abalina obutali bulongoofu eri enkola ya renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) oba endwadde ezirimu obuwuka bwa angiotensin II obuyitiridde. Okuteeka eddagala lya rhACE2 mu kkolero ly'ekisawo mu bujjanjabi bw'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'omu nsawo.
COVID-19 ye programu ya ssimu ey'omulembe eyakolebwa okuyamba mu kunoonyereza ku nkolagana mu bulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019-20, gamba ng'okuzuula abantu ("ennamba") abayinza okuba nga baaliko akakwate n'omuntu alina obulwadde.
Enkola nnyingi zaakolebwa oba zaaweebwa abantu bangi, nga ziwagirwa gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu n'ebitundu.
Enkola ez'okuzimba ez'enjawulo ez'okutegeera abantu zeezimbiddwa.
Okweraliikirira ku kwonoona obuntu bwa muntu kwalagibwa, naddala ku nkola ez'okumanya ebifo by'omukozesa.
Engeri endala ey'obuteefiirayo eri mu kukozesa Bluetooth okuteekawo omukutu ogukwatagana n'essimu endala ng'okozesa programu eri okumpi.
Nga 10 Apuli 2020, Google ne Apple baategeezezza nti bagenda kutandikawo programu eno okuwagira programu ez'oku mutimbagano ez'oku mutimbagano ez'oku mutimbagano ez'oku mutimbagano ez'oku Android ne iOS.
Mu China, Gavumenti ya China, ng'ekolagana ne Alipay, yatandikawo programu esobozesa abantu okumanya oba nga baaliko akakwate n'abantu abalina COVID-19.
Ekikozesebwa mu bibuga ebisukka mu 200 mu China. Mu Singapore, programu eyitibwa TraceTogether ekozesebwa.
Enkola eno ekoleddwa ekibiina ky'abanoonyereza ku by'obujjanjabi n'eby'obuweereza, era eteekeddwawo ng'ensulo y'obubaka eri abantu bonna era nga esobola okuweebwa gavumenti. North Macedonia yafulumya "StopKorona!", programu ekozesa Bluetooth okumanya oba oli kumpi n'abantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi era n'okuwa abakungu b'ebyobulamu eky'okuddamu ekyangu.
Enkola eno yatandikibwawo minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'entekinologiya ne minisitule y'ebyobulamu.
Okuva nga 14 April 2020, programu eno erina okussibwa mu Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 omwezi gwa Apuli, Gavumenti yategeeza nti programu eno ey'okumanya omuntu yali mu mitendera egy'okusingawo mu kutandika era yali egenda kuba esobola okusaasaanyizibwa mu wiiki eziddako. Enkola ng'eyo etegekeddwa mu Ireland, ne mu Bufalansa ("StopCovid").
Australia ne New Zealand zirowooza ku kutandikawo programu z'amasimu nga zigoberera ekyokulabirako kya TraceTogether eya Singapore ne BlueTrace eya Russia. Russia eteekateeka okutandikawo programu ez'okukuuma abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu Moscow nga balamu bulungi.
Ross Anderson, Profesa mu by'okukozesa ebyokwerinda mu yunivasite ya Cambridge, yalaga obuzibu obutali bumu obuyinza okuva mu nkola ez'okuteeka mu ssimu, omuli obubonero bw'obulwadde n'obutaba bulungi bw'obuntu bw'abantu abatono.
Okukendeeza ku kweraliikirira ku kubuna kwa programu ez'obukuusa oba ez'akabi ez'okulondoola obulwadde bwa coronavirus, Apple eremesezza abantu ab'enjawulo okusindika programu ez'okulondoola obulwadde bwa coronavirus mu App Store, nga bakkiriza "enkola ezikkirizibwa mu butongole" oba mu ngeri endala, ebibiina ebyesigika.
Google ne Amazon nabyo bitaddewo amateeka ag'enjawulo.
Abantu kinnoomu baalaga nti beeraliikirivu olw'okukebera abantu bangi nga bakozesa tekinologiya wa ssimu, naddala bwe kiba nti enkola ez'okwekebera obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe zijja kuggibwawo ng'ekirwadde kiwedde.
Amnesty International n'ebibiina ebirala ebisukka mu 100 baakuba akalulu nga basaba okukendeeza ku nkola eno ey'okwetegereza.
