buli kiwandiiko ky'amawulire kirina okuba nga kyesigamiziddwa ku mateeka;
ebikolwa eby'obukambwe birina okuteekebwawo era n'abantu basobole okubyerekereza;
"Kyenkwaso nnyo" ky'okwenyigira kwa buli "mukozi" omutuufu, omuli abakugu mu by'obujjanjabi n'ebibinja by'abantu abawugulibwa, ekitongole kya tekinologiya ekya Germany (CCC) ne RSF nabyo byalaga olukalala lw'ebintu eby'okukola.
Enteekateeka eya Google/Apple ey'okulaga obuzibu bw'okunoonyereza ku bujjuvu esazeewo okuggyawo obubonero bw'abantu abafunye akawuka mu nkola zaabwe ng'obubonero obwo tebukyetaagisa.
Amawanga agamu gaakozesa enkola y'okunoonya abantu mu kifo kya tekinologiya wa ssimu, nga kino kiviirako obwetaavu bw'okukozesa tekinologiya wa ssimu n'obutasobola kunoonyezebwa.
